dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.res.vnrole.ResourceInstaller
dataStructure.description:
This class represents the role of installing PhysicalResources. It specifically doesn't provide all of the capabilities of a Technician role, but also represents a less costly PartyRole. Specifically, a ResourceInstaller is limited to simple physical installation of Equipment. A ResourceInstaller does not configure Resources or Services.

This entity is optional
dataStructure.label: ResourceInstaller
